# Nexora Frontend — environment variables
#
# Dev mode (default): leave unset.
#   The Vite dev server proxies /api/* → http://127.0.0.1:8000, so
#   requests are same-origin and CORS is not needed.
#
# Production mode: set this to your deployed backend base URL,
#   e.g. https://api.nexora.example.com
#   The URL must NOT end with /api (the client appends /health, /query, etc.)
#   Your production reverse proxy must add the appropriate CORS headers.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
